          <title>
            <string language="en">The food web of the American crayfish</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Das Nahrungsmittelweb der amerikanischen 
Panzerkrebse</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Le Web de nourriture des écrevisses américaines</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">O Web do alimento das lagostas americanas</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Il Web dell'alimento degli astaci americani</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Ο Ιστός τροφίμων των αμερικανικών αστακών</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">El Web del alimento de los cangrejos americanos</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This diagram shows that the abundance of living things on which the American crayfish depend for food has ensured its survival and propagation.</string>
          </description>
          <language>x-none</language>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">american crayfish</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">predator</string>
          </keyword>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <structure>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Dieses Diagramm zeigt, daß der Überfluß an 
lebenden Sachen, von denen die amerikanischen Panzerkrebse für 
Nahrung abhängen, sein Überleben und Ausbreitung sichergestellt hat.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Ce diagramme prouve que l'abondance de choses 
vivantes desquelles les écrevisses américaines dépendent pour la 
nourriture a assuré sa survie et propagation.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Este diagrama mostra que a abundância de coisas 
vivas de que as lagostas americanas dependem para o alimento assegurou
suas sobrevivência e propagação.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questo schema indica che l'abbondanza delle cose 
viventi da cui gli astaci americani dipendono per alimento ha 
accertato la relative sopravvivenza e propagazione.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτό το διάγραμμα δείχνει ότι η αφθονία πραγμάτων 
διαβίωσης από την οποία οι αμερικανικοί αστακοί εξαρτώνται για 
τα τρόφιμα έχει εξασφαλίσει την επιβίωση και τη διάδοσή της.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Este diagrama muestra que la abundancia de las 
cosas vivas de las cuales los cangrejos americanos dependen para el 
alimento ha asegurado su supervivencia y propagación.</string>
          </description>
